commitResults.messageTitle: Add function to copy a contact's information to clipboard
commitResults.messageBody:
Add "clip" function to allow users to efficiently copy a contact's information onto their system's clipboard with a simple command.

Add new classes to facilitate this feature, including:
* Predicate class to search for exact Name String matching (as compared to sub-string matching used in "find" command)
* Function to compare Name String which ignores casing
* Parser class for parsing of this command
* Unit tests for new classes created
